---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="container page-content">
		<h1 class="page-title">About the Project</h1>
		<div class="content-wrapper">
			<p class="intro">
				The RdRp Summit is a collaborative initiative dedicated to the study of RNA-dependent RNA polymerase (RdRp).
				Our goal is to bring together researchers from around the world to share knowledge, data, and tools.
			</p>
			
			<hr class="divider" />
			
			<h2>Mission</h2>
			<p>
				We aim to provide a comprehensive resource for the classification, discovery, and analysis of RdRp sequences
				from diverse environments. By standardizing methods and data formats, we facilitate easier comparison
				and meta-analysis across different studies.
			</p>

			<h2>History</h2>
			<p>
				Started as a small workshop, the RdRp Summit has grown into a global community. 
				We hold regular meetings and maintain this centralized repository of information.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-content {
		max-width: 720px; /* Narrower for better reading experience */
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.page-title {
		margin-top: 40px;
		margin-bottom: 40px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.content-wrapper {
		font-size: 19px; /* Slightly larger reading text */
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #333;
	}

	.intro {
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--c-text);
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	.divider {
		border: 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--c-divider);
		margin: 40px 0;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-top: 40px;
		font-size: 28px;
	}
</style>
